# Product Satisfaction Survey
# Help us understand your experience with our product

> start "Thank you for purchasing from us! Please take a moment to share your experience." "Product Feedback" -> q1

? q1 Ch* "Which product did you purchase?" [
  a: "Product A - Basic" = product_a,
  b: "Product B - Standard" = product_b,
  c: "Product C - Premium" = product_c
] -> q2

? q2 Rt* "Rate the overall quality" {min: 1, max: 5} -> q3

? q3 Rt* "Rate the value for money" {min: 1, max: 5} -> q4

? q4 Lk* "The product met my expectations" {scale: 5, start: "Strongly Disagree", end: "Strongly Agree"} -> q5

? q5 Mc* "What features do you like most?" [
  design: "Design & Aesthetics" = design,
  ease: "Ease of Use" = ease,
  performance: "Performance" = performance,
  durability: "Durability" = durability,
  price: "Price Point" = price
] {maxSelections: 3} -> q6

? q6 Tx "Any suggestions for improvement?" {placeholder: "Share your ideas (optional)"} -> end

< end "Thank you for your valuable feedback!" "Survey Complete"
